description:
SUMMER VENGEANCE MATCH
MADISON YOUNG
The Butcher
HT: 5'2
WT: 109lbs
Lifetime record (2-1)
Ranked 9th
SAFARI
Safari
HT: 5'7
WT: 130lbs
Lifetime record (0-1)
Ranked 10th
Welcome to the second annual Summer Vengeance elimination tournament. The top sixteen Season Five wrestlers battle it out to see who will be the overall Ultimate Surrender champion for 2008.
Madison was injured and on the DL list for most of the season. Now she is back 100% healthy and ranked 9th. Madison is strong fast, tenacious, and on of the toughest wrestlers on the roster.
Safari has only had one match but it was an impressive match against veteran. Impressive enough to earn the number 10 spot in the tournament. Pound for Pound Safari is probably the strongest wrestler in the tournament, and she has the fury to drive that power.
Join today and get in on the ground floor of the 2008 Championship Tournament that will end with one overall Champion!
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE CONTINUES! This is the last elimination match of the first round.
